</paragraph>
<paragraph id="215A368EEB448B024CA44216FD15FD89" blockId="3.[136,702,522,652]" box="[136,702,558,580]" pageId="3" pageNumber="297">
‘Cido Abava’— 
<bibRefCitation id="45744B7FEB448B024D0E4216FE0DFD89" author="Tics, A." box="[290,422,558,580]" pageId="3" pageNumber="297" refId="ref5823" refString="Tics, A. (2000) Ziemelu citrons Cido. Jauna auglu kultura. [author's edition], [Pure], 257 pp." type="book" year="2000">Tīcs 2000: 38</bibRefCitation>
(description), 
